Factorial of a number
Remya is studying in 10th std and she was not good at maths. Her maths teacher asked to find a factorial of the given number. Can you help Remya by writing a program for the same.
Input Format:

The input consist of an integer

Output Format:

Print the factorial of a number which denotes an integer

Sample Input:

5

Sample Output:

120



Case 1
Case 2
Case 3
Input (stdin)
6

Output (stdout)
720

Input (stdin)
8

Output (stdout)
40320

Input (stdin)
3

Output (stdout)
6

PROGRAM IN CPP

#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() 
{
  int n, fact=1;
  cin>>n;
  for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
  {
    fact = fact*i;
  }
  cout<<fact;
  return 0;
}
